{"name":"Dretch","size":"large","type":"fey","tag":"","alignment":"chaotic evil","hitDice":"8","armorName":"natural armor","shieldBonus":0,"natArmorBonus":1,"otherArmorDesc":"11","speed":"25","burrowSpeed":"0","climbSpeed":"0","flySpeed":"0","hover":false,"swimSpeed":"40","customHP":false,"customSpeed":false,"hpText":"52 (8d10 + 8)","speedDesc":"20 ft., swim 40 ft.","strPoints":"15","dexPoints":"13","conPoints":"13","intPoints":"2","wisPoints":"10","chaPoints":"3","blindsight":"0","blind":false,"darkvision":"60","tremorsense":"0","truesight":"0","telepathy":0,"cr":"1","customCr":"1 (200 XP)","customProf":2,"isLegendary":false,"legendariesDescription":"The giant toad can take 3 legendary actions, choosing from the options below. Only one legendary action option can be used at a time and only at the end of another creature's turn. The giant toad regains spent legendary actions at the start of its turn.","isLair":false,"lairDescription":"When fighting inside its lair, the giant toad can invoke the ambient magic to take lair actions. On initiative count 20 (losing initiative ties), the giant toad can take one lair action to cause one of the following effects:","lairDescriptionEnd":"The giant toad can't repeat an effect until they have all been used, and it can't use the same effect two rounds in a row.","isMythic":false,"mythicDescription":"If the giant toad's mythic trait is active, it can use the options below as legendary actions for 1 hour after using {Some Ability}.","isRegional":false,"regionalDescription":"The region containing the giant toad's lair is warped by the creature's presence, which creates one or more of the following effects:","regionalDescriptionEnd":"If the giant toad dies, the first two effects fade over the course of 3d10 days.","properties":[],"abilities":[{"name":"Amphibious","desc":"The dretch can breathe air and water"},{"name":"Aggregate Abomination","desc":"The first time the dretch takes damage when it is below 39 HP, it splits into 3 CR 1/4 \ndretchlings."}],"actions":[{"name":"Bite","desc":"_Melee Weapon Attack:_ +4 to hit, reach 5 ft., one target. _Hit:_ 5 (1d6 + 1) piercing damage plus 2 (1d4) poison damage, and the target is grappled (escape DC 13). Until this grapple ends, the target is restrained, and the toad can't bite another target."},{"name":"Swallow","desc":"The dretch makes one bite attack against a Medium or smaller target it is grappling. If the attack hits, the target is swallowed, and the grapple ends. The swallowed target is blinded and restrained, it has total cover against attacks and other effects outside the dretch, and it takes 7 (2d6) poison damage at the start of each of the dretch's turns. The dretch can have only one target swallowed at a time.\nIf the dretch dies or splits, a swallowed creature is no longer restrained by it and can escape from the corpse using 5 feet of movement, exiting prone."},{"name":"Tongue Lash","desc":"_Ranged Weapon Attack:_ +4 to hit, reach 20 ft., one target. _Hit:_ 2 (1d4) piercing damage plus 2 (1d4) poison damage, and the target is pulled 20ft towards the creature and grappled (escape DC 13). Until this grapple ends, the target is restrained, and the toad can't bite another target."},{"name":"Fetid Cloud","desc":"(1/Day). A 20-foot radius of disgusting green gas extends out from the dretch. The gas spreads around corners, and its area is lightly obscured. It lasts for 1 minute or until a strong wind disperses it. Any creature that starts its turn in that area must succeed on a DC 11 Constitution saving throw or be poisoned until the start of its next turn. While poisoned in this way, the target can take either an action or a bonus action on its turn, not both, and can't take reactions."}],"bonusActions":[],"reactions":[],"legendaries":[],"mythics":[],"lairs":[],"regionals":[],"sthrows":[],"skills":[],"damagetypes":[{"name":"acid","note":" (Vulnerable)","type":"v"},{"name":"cold","note":" (Resistant)","type":"r"},{"name":"poison","note":" (Immune)","type":"i"}],"specialdamage":[],"conditions":[{"name":"poisoned"}],"languages":[],"understandsBut":"","shortName":"","pluralName":"","doubleColumns":false,"separationPoint":1,"damage":[]}